===转录===
线粒体DNA进行[[多顺反子|多顺反子]]转录，一次会有多个基因一同被转录，之后剪切酶会将转录本进行切割加工，将mRNA、rRNA，以及位于mRNA序列之间的短小tRNA序列从初始转录本上切下<ref name="GallaherCraig2021">{{cite journal|last1=Gallaher|first1=Sean D.|last2=Craig|first2=Rory J.|last3=Ganesan|first3=Iniyan|last4=Purvine|first4=Samuel O.|last5=McCorkle|first5=Sean R.|last6=Grimwood|first6=Jane|last7=Strenkert|first7=Daniela|last8=Davidi|first8=Lital|last9=Roth|first9=Melissa S.|last10=Jeffers|first10=Tim L.|last11=Lipton|first11=Mary S.|last12=Niyogi|first12=Krishna K.|last13=Schmutz|first13=Jeremy|last14=Theg|first14=Steven M.|last15=Blaby-Haas|first15=Crysten E.|last16=Merchant|first16=Sabeeha S.|title=Widespread polycistronic gene expression in green algae|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume=118|issue=7|year=2021|pages=e2017714118|issn=0027-8424|doi=10.1073/pnas.2017714118}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Falkenberg M, Larsson NG, Gustafsson CM | title = DNA replication and transcription in mammalian mitochondria | journal = Annual Review of Biochemistry | volume = 76 | issue = 1 | pages = 679–99 | date = 2007-06-19 | pmid = 17408359 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.biochem.76.060305.152028 }}</ref>。

